---
title: Digireceipt - Tickets de caisse, reçus, factures et notes de frais numérisés
---

<div id="banner" class="smooth-scrollable">

  <div class="fade-and-slide text-center">
    <h1>Ne perdez plus jamais vos tickets de caisse</h1>
    <br>
    <p>Digireceipt est la nouvelle manière de collecter et sauvegarder ses tickets de caisse,
    <br>reçus de carte et factures directement depuis son smartphone.</p>
    <br>
    <br>
    <a href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#subscribe-modal" class="btn-medium">ÊTRE INFORMÉ DU LANCEMENT</a>
  </div>

  <a href="#description"><i class="fa fa-angle-down fa-6 pulse scroll-btn"></i></a>
</div>

<div class="bg-white padded" id="description">
  <div class="container text-center" id="features">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
        <div class="card" data-sr="enter bottom and scale up 20% over 1s">
          <%= image_tag "paper.svg" %>
          <h2>Natural writing</h2>
          <p>Don't change your habits, write with a pen <strong>on paper notebooks</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
        <div class="card" data-sr="enter bottom and scale up 20% over 1.5s">
          <%= image_tag "computer.svg" %>
          <h2>Sync. copy</h2>
          <p>Stylus instantaneously copy your text on your computer, <strong>in real-time</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
        <div class="card" data-sr="enter bottom and scale up 20% over 2s">
          <%= image_tag "analytics.svg" %>
          <h2>Analytics</h2>
          <p>Get feedbacks on the way you write, <strong>your favorite words, your frequent mistakes</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
        <div class="card" data-sr="enter bottom and scale up 20% over 2.5s">
          <%= image_tag "data.svg" %>
          <h2>Storing your texts</h2>
          <p>Every line writen with your stylus is stored in the cloud, so that <strong>it's never lost</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="padded container text-center">
    <p>Leave us your mail and get stylus news</p>
    <form class="form-inline">
      <input type="email" placeholder="bob@gmail.com" class="form-control">
      <input type="submit" value="Subscribe" class="btn btn-primary btn-bordered btn-bordered-primary">
    </form>
  </div>
</div>